Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.52,0:00:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}On the first day we moved\Nto our new flat,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.65,0:00:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}at the residents' association\Nmeeting...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.37,0:00:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- Do you want to kill me?\N- Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.88,0:00:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}And our conversation started.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.28,0:00:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Everyone has a moment
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}that they want to kill someone\Nor just want them dead, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I want to kill them\Nif I wouldn't be caught,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.13,0:00:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}but I will, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.29,0:00:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}The police first checks\Nif there is someone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.45,0:00:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}among the people the victim\Nknew had a motive to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.92,0:00:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}So if someone has no motive,\Nthey won't be caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I think it'd be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.12,0:00:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Then no one will find out if we swap\Nthe targets we want to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.52,0:00:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It's murder-swap, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.09,0:00:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Why don't we reveal it together?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.13,0:00:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}Before I realised,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.33,0:00:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}it turned into a game that we tell\Neach other who we want to kill.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.33,0:00:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Do not show other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.93,0:00:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Now, open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}I thought it was a silly joke...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.01,0:00:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Takafumi Kono"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.81,0:00:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}But on that night...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.77,0:01:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Our property manager”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.88,0:01:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}You mean he suddenly fell down?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.23,0:01:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Sumida Police Station detective,\NMasato Kamiya"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.87,0:01:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Yes. I had no idea\Nthat it was a man at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.08,0:01:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}so I was shocked\Nwhen I went outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.31,0:01:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Where was your husband at that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.71,0:01:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}He is on a business trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Good evening, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Mr Mizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.60,0:01:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- Is he dead?\N- Would you like to check?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Idiot! It's scary!\NIt's fine if you've checked.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:01:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Sumida Police Station detective,\NYouji Mizuki"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.44,0:02:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.44,0:02:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- have you checked the roof?\N- Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.84,0:02:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}There was no trace of struggle,\Nso it could be suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.84,0:02:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}If it's the case,\Nhe could've fallen anywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.28,0:02:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}but he fell in front of this flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Does it mean anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.39,0:02:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- Sir, will you go to the roof--\N- I said I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.72,0:02:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- Mr Kamiya.\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.29,0:02:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Room 402, Masashi Enomoto"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.95,0:02:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Room 302, Nana Tezuka"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Room 302, Shota Tezuka"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.03,0:02:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- Maybe I should take a day off?\N- Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.11,0:02:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}You must feel helpless on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I know I should mind\Nmy own business,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.59,0:02:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}but this happened on\Nthe first day you moved here,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.91,0:02:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}so I thought you must be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:03:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Yes, I am worried, but I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.11,0:03:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Well, I'm the chairlady\Nof the residents' association,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}but we take turns to do it\Nso I guess you can't count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Don't say that.\NThank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.28,0:03:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}By the way, it was suicide, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Why? Could he have been killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}No, it's just there are\Nso many police officers here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Indeed! If in the unlikely case\Nthat it was murder, this--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- Oh, aren't you going to be late?\N- But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Sanae is here and I really am fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.87,0:03:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Okay then, I'll go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- See you.\N- Thank you, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- See you.\N- See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Nana, do you have to go to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.83,0:03:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I work at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.71,0:03:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It's shocking to know\Nthat someone I know died.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}And he killed himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Yes, he killed himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Yes. It's upsetting\Nthat he killed himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.19,0:04:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Ground floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.36,0:04:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Obey the rules properly”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Our property manager”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Room 403, Atsushi Fujii"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.19,0:04:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}The tough time continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}Dr Yamagiwa, is there any\Nbreakthrough in the treatment?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}Well, I'm a doctor,\Nso I shouldn't say this,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}but you can only treat the symptoms\Nof hay fever when they appear.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}For example--{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I'll go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Ground floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.03,0:04:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Manager's office"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:05:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Room 204, Jun Nishimura"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Maybe I should attend the next\Nresidents' association meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}You and the chairlady seemed close,\Nand I am jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It's not fair that only you\Nbecame friends with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.14,0:05:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}We played Werewolf\Nand became friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}You don't actually want to attend,\Nright? I'll go next time too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Mr Tezuka, the members are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Sorry, coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:05:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Let's get fired up and be friends\Nwith our muscles today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- Okay.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Our property manager"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:07:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Your Turn to Kill"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Episode 2"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Touo University Hospital"\NCome again a week later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.26,0:07:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- Take care.\N- Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.38,0:07:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Nurse, Ruri Sakuragi"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}Schlecken!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- Dr Fujii.\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}You think I don't know if you say\Nsomething dirty in German?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What did I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}You always do that, that's why\Nyou can never get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Oh, what you just said\Nwas more insulting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.77,0:07:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}If you appear on TV,\Nmaybe you'll get a bit popular
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.05,0:07:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}like Doctor Yamagiwa,\Nwho is popular lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.65,0:07:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Don't lump me in\Nwith Yutaro Yamagiwa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}You know his full name?\NAre you a fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.57,0:08:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Of course I am not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It beeps every day\Nand it's so noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Sorry, I'm practising\Nhow to reverse my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}You can't drive at all.\NDon't drive a car better than mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.93,0:08:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Amulet"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Tokoshima"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Mr Mizuki, I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.37,0:08:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}He wrote a suicide note?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:08:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}No, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:09:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Hey, sprinkle some salt\Nbefore you come close!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It's a hospital's\Nmedical certificate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.17,0:09:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Disease: Brain tumor"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.93,0:09:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Seems that he had a brain tumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}He gave in to despair\Nand killed himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.94,0:09:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}By the way, about the manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Don't talk about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.86,0:09:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}No. I think it wasn't suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Just drop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}But a murder doesn't happen\Nso close to us every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}The case is worth deducing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.69,0:09:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It's not appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Why? Isn't it more inappropriate
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.02,0:09:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}to let the real culprit\Ngo unpunished?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I think we should seek the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}The police said it was suicide,\Nthen it's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.33,0:09:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}The truth is,\Nit's always the orangutan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- You get it, right?\N- I do, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}So listen to me, great detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:09:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Stop calling me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I have almost found out the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It'll get cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}The real culprit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.33,0:10:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Room 301's Ono!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.81,0:10:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Room 301, Mikiha Ono"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.73,0:10:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Our next door?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I checked all the flats just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Only Room 301's Ono actually uses\Nthe name plate made by the manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}So maybe they were\Nin a relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.33,0:10:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Their relationship turned ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Thanks for supper.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}How was my suspicion?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Look! It's bull's-eye!\NDon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.22,0:10:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Are you worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}But if something bad happened,\Nsomething good must happen too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.94,0:11:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.42,0:11:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Yes, the leaflet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}The food allergens aren't written,\Nwhat do you think about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.89,0:11:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}No, no need to call your manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I only want to know what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Ground floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Is everybody there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Misato, Mr Tamiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Room 104, Yoko Ishizaki"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I've called Miss Ono here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.65,0:11:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- Thank you.\N- Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.13,0:11:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Sorry, we're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}There are even fewer of us\Nthan last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- Mrs Enomoto.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.81,0:11:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Room 103, Junichiro Tamiya"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.73,0:12:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}We suddenly asked you to come today
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.65,0:12:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}to talk about our property manager,\NMr Tokoshima.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Should our residents' association\Nsend flowers to his funeral?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}You called us here just for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.49,0:12:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}He had been helping us.\NNo need to check and just send them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.57,0:12:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}We'll use the reserve,\Nso we'd better check first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.03,0:12:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Let's vote to make the decision\Nnow, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.53,0:12:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}But will 2 funerals be held?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Of course there'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.17,0:12:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Room 101, Yuzuru Kuzumi"\NBut...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.25,0:12:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Even for someone who killed himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Mr Fujii, what you said wasn't nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Of course, I agree\Nthat we should send flowers,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}but how much gift money\Nshould we send?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Let's discuss the amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Room 502, Misato Akaike"\NWhy don't we send a sum together?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}But how much per person?\NLet's agree on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:13:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Mr Tamiya worked at a bank.\NLet's ask him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}My former job isn't related.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.83,0:13:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}But you must've been to many\Nfunerals of small company owners
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}who killed themselves\Nbecause you didn't lend them money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}You've been acting mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.07,0:13:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Room 203, Xinyi"\NTamiya, you're always so unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Xinyi, Mr Tamiya didn't say\Nanything funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I got it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}How can you smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}He could've been killed\Nbecause of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Because of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.36,0:13:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}If you hadn't said the police would\Nnot find out about murder-swap,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.24,0:13:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}we wouldn't have told each other\Nwho we wanted to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.60,0:13:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I didn't suggest the murder-swap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.68,0:13:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Wait. First of all, none of us wrote\Nthe property manager, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}He was so close to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.15,0:13:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}This was pinned on the notice board.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Our property manager"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.23,0:14:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Whose handwriting is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Will you drop this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.71,0:14:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}But this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Put yourselves in the shoes\Nof the person who wrote it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.55,0:14:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}They wrote the manager's name\Nas a joke,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.83,0:14:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}but he happened to kill himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I'm sure that the person\Ncan't describe how they feel now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.44,0:14:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}You are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}That's why\Nthey can't attend today...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}That means it was Mrs Kitagawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Room 304, Sumika Kitagawa"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}We don't know who wrote it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}In the end,\Nwe all happily wrote a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.08,0:14:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}We're all accomplices.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.04,0:14:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Don't say that! I am not involved!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.88,0:14:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- I am not either!\N- Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.52,0:14:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}This is not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Let's throw it away. Give me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What? Do you suspect me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Just so you know,\NI wrote Yutaro Yamagiwa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Could you possibly mean\NDoctor Yamagiwa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Dr Yamagiwa (Yutaro Yamagiwa)\NDirector of Yamagiwa Medical Clinic"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.73,0:15:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}He appears on TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.09,0:15:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}The doctor is a pundit\Non talk shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Yamagiwa was my classmate\Nin college.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I've always hated him so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}that I wanted to pull his head off\Nmany times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.85,0:15:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Okay. I said it honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Whose name did you guys write?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Manager's office"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Why don't you say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}You guys are a lot more suspicious\Nthan me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Stop it, Mr Fujii.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.97,0:16:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}So as I thought,\Nit wasn't a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}The man was murdered\Nby someone among you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- I said...\N- By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}let's say that one of you\Nwrote "Our property manager" here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Someone killed the man\Nthat you want dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}so you have to kill the person\Non the piece of paper you drew,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}or you'll violate the rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Nobody mentioned this rule!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}But you made someone\Ntake the risk for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}how can you stay safe yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Wait. We did write the name\Nof the person we want dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}we didn't tell anyone to kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.64,0:16:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Well, that woman said you wouldn't\Nbe caught if it was a murder-swap,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.84,0:16:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}so someone took it seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I said, I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- What are you doing?\N- Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}We all get suspicious\Nbecause of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- It's evidence...\N- I'll eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.49,0:17:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- Gosh!\N- Mr Tamiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.69,0:17:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What are you doing? Spit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}He swallowed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.49,0:17:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Nobody in this residential tower\Nis a murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.17,0:17:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- You know...\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.65,0:17:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I don't like to gossip,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}but Mr Tamiya is too serious
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}and many things happened\Nto him at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}He was made to resign early\Nbecause of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Even now, his serious power\Nhas gotten too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.09,0:17:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Have a good evening...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Please move the tables to the edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.73,0:17:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Please move this there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- Excuse me.\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I'll give you back the 1,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Room 202, Sawa Kuroshima"\NThanks for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.41,0:17:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- Well...\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}This is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.69,0:18:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.01,0:18:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It is cute, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.09,0:18:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.93,0:18:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}He's my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.93,0:18:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.05,0:18:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}The window is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.17,0:18:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.93,0:18:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.37,0:18:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}The window!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.81,0:18:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Masashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.21,0:18:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.79,0:19:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}So... I was passing by\Nwhen I saw the broken window.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I think some of you don't know,\Nbut I am a police officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}So I've been checking\Nthe office again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Gosh, you startled me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.54,0:19:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I thought it was\NMr Tokoshima's ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I did frighten you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Sorry for bringing you trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.95,0:19:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Oh, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.80,0:19:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}In the end, our property manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}We inspected his home\Nand found that he had a disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}In other words?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}He killed himself\Nafter worrying for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}At least, we think\Nthat it wasn't a murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.30,0:19:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It was suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}We had no idea\Nthat he had a disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I knew it!\NI thought his face was pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.16,0:20:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Everyone,\NI know you must be worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Room 401, Akane Kinoshita"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Anyway, shouldn't you have been\Na bit more helpful?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.62,0:20:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Don't just say sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.94,0:20:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Why do I have to be suspected?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Because of that,\Nthat Central Circular Route and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It's so annoying.\NGo and switch it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.24,0:20:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}From the Gotanda part\Nof the inner route{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}of the Central Circular Route,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}vehicles in front\Nof Hey Junction...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- Hey...\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.84,0:20:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Did you keep the receipt\Nof our dinner last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Receipt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.32,0:20:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}You talk too loudly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.08,0:20:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Receipt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.76,0:20:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Receipt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- Receipt.\N- Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}This?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.16,0:21:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Now we have an alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}At the time that the manager died,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}we were having dinner outside.\NIt's the unmistakable truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.24,0:21:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Does the police suspect us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.20,0:21:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}No, nobody suspects us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.49,0:21:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}But! I'm saying, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I don't know who will try to frame\Nme at this period of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.79,0:21:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I'll cause everyone in\Nthe deputy chief's faction trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Do you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Until our faction wins,\NI have to do everything carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.53,0:21:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Chiunque Kuramae"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}After the property manager's funeral\Nwas held,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.01,0:21:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}we took back the peaceful life\Nwe had until then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.48,0:22:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- See you!\N- See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.28,0:22:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- Good morning.\N- Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.00,0:22:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Hurry up, Sora! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.48,0:22:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.60,0:22:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.88,0:22:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}The property manager's death\Nwas sad,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.40,0:22:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}but when nothing happens\Nin our daily life,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.08,0:22:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}it becomes the power\Nthat helps us overcome sadness,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.44,0:22:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}and we all know that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.48,0:22:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Room 201, Ryo Kakinuma"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Watch it! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.48,0:22:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Hurry up! I'll cut your neck next.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.96,0:22:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- It will get messy soon anyway.\N- Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.44,0:22:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.68,0:22:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}The day is getting longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.28,0:22:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It looks like the setting sun\Nin Van Gogh's painting, Misato.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.48,0:22:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Van Gogh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.52,0:22:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Room 502, Sachiko Akaike,\NGoro Akaike"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.40,0:22:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.52,0:23:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Sower with Setting Sun?\NIt's a nice painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.04,0:23:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Misato could almost remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.28,0:23:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- Oh, I'm sorry.\N- It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.52,0:23:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Speaking of setting sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.52,0:23:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"The zinc roofing\Neats a rice cracker..."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}And then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.52,0:23:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.32,0:23:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Chuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.18,0:23:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It's Chuya Nakahara's poem.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.44,0:23:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Ashes being thrown underhanded\Ngo pale."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.64,0:23:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}And?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.12,0:23:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Go pale...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.04,0:23:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"It is quiet\Nwhen the sun sets in spring."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.20,0:23:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.88,0:23:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Misato was just going to answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.08,0:23:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.88,0:23:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}The poem was written in\Na middle school textbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.20,0:23:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}How can Misato not know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.92,0:23:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I wasn't good at\NJapanese literature.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.32,0:23:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Oh, I am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.24,0:23:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Your Japanese is worse than\Na middle school child.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.24,0:24:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I had no idea. Will you forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.96,0:24:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.48,0:24:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Glad to hear that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.72,0:24:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.80,0:24:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It's nice that\Nyou're always so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.16,0:24:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Thank you! I roll with laughter\Nevery single day!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.28,0:24:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.16,0:24:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Oh, hey?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.72,0:25:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Mr Tezuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.68,0:25:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- Oh! Hello.\N- Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.66,0:25:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- What's the matter?\N- Nothing, your hair accessory...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.60,0:25:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.68,0:25:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.32,0:25:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It looks so good on me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.42,0:25:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}You praised me. I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.08,0:25:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}So maybe it isn't exactly\Na thank you gift...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.13,0:25:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.52,0:25:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Wafers.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.28,0:25:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.49,0:25:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.77,0:25:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I've never seen anyone\Nmake wafers themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.73,0:26:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It isn't cut, so maybe\Nit's difficult to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.97,0:26:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- May I?\N- Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.41,0:26:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.25,0:26:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- It's good!\N- It is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.77,0:26:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I made it with organic rice flour.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.13,0:26:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I haven't tried this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.49,0:26:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Is there anything\Nthat you have never tried before?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.69,0:26:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It can be anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.73,0:26:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I want to be your first, Mr Tezuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.49,0:26:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What the heck? You're funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.45,0:26:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}But it's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.41,0:26:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.54,0:26:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Yes, there are three\Nof each color pattern,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.22,0:26:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}so there are 21 patterns in total.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.38,0:26:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Yes. If you would check it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.70,0:26:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.54,0:27:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Sanae?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.70,0:27:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Sorry, I shouldn't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.42,0:27:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Reversing a car is difficult\Nuntil you get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.26,0:27:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Okay, it's parked.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.66,0:27:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.38,0:27:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I feel so ashamed of myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.38,0:27:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Mr Tezuka,\Nyour new customer is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.05,0:27:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.49,0:27:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.53,0:27:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Mr Hosokawa,\Nwho applied for our personal plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.05,0:27:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Yes, I'm Hosokawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.61,0:27:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Asao Hosokawa"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.61,0:28:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Your goal is to keep yourself fit,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.13,0:28:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}so we'll tighten your waistline\Nafter you get used to it a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.17,0:28:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Sure. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.29,0:28:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.13,0:28:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Okay, let's begin our first step.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.73,0:28:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Please call me Sho\Nwhen we're doing the training.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.87,0:28:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- Sho?\N- Yes, Sho.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.19,0:28:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}But may I say no?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.34,0:28:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Does it make you shy?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.06,0:28:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Does anybody not feel shy?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.91,0:28:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}But during training,\Nyour body will be under stress,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.91,0:28:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}it'll be difficult to call me\N“trainer” or "Mr Tezuka".
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.55,0:28:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}So we'll keep our names short.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.59,0:28:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}My name is Shota,\Nso please call me Sho.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.39,0:28:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Now, say "Sho"!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.35,0:28:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Sho.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.19,0:28:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.55,0:28:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Sho.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.35,0:28:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Say it louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.61,0:28:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Sho!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.41,0:28:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Three times!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.53,0:28:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Sho! Sho! Sho!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.53,0:28:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Okay, let's do some stretching!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.49,0:28:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Then, the new customer said
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.69,0:28:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}that he loved detective stories,\Nso I was really happy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.57,0:29:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What should I lend him?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.54,0:29:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Don't tell him how it ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.33,0:29:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}When you recommend someone\Na detective story you like,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.73,0:29:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}you say the ending first.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.30,0:29:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.50,0:29:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.02,0:29:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}The murderer was shot up to the sky\Nwith the fireworks
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.02,0:29:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}and died in pieces mid-air!"
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.74,0:29:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}You said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.74,0:29:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}That was the best final scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.42,0:29:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}But I couldn't enjoy it\Nbecause I knew how it'd end.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.18,0:29:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.50,0:29:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.42,0:29:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.82,0:29:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Oh, I bought it for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.06,0:29:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It's a coffee maker.\NIts design is good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.34,0:29:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Yeah. How much was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.62,0:29:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}A bit over 30,000 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.90,0:29:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It's expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.46,0:29:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I stay at home all day,\Nit's capital investment.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.10,0:29:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}You did it again.\NIt's your bad habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.18,0:29:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}You use difficult words to try\Nto draw away my attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.85,0:29:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}No, capital investment\Naren't difficult words.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.49,0:29:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Moreover, I paid it myself. Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.45,0:29:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What? I didn't say it\Nbecause I have no money.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.86,0:29:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Sorry. What is it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.01,0:30:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Yes, indeed,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.53,0:30:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I can't pay half of the sum of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.85,0:30:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I can't. But you've bought it.\NSo I'll pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.69,0:30:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Because we own it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.18,0:30:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I want everything in our flat\Nto be our common property.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.65,0:30:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I'll buy things after asking you\Nnext time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.25,0:30:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}That's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.69,0:30:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It is true that the amounts\Nof our income are different,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.21,0:30:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}but I don't want you to consider\Nmy feelings and my income
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.69,0:30:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}and hold yourself back\Nfrom buying things you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.85,0:30:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It makes me sad\Nif you're considerate in that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.37,0:30:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}But I don't want you to buy things\Nwithout considering me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.78,0:30:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}So just get something I can pay\Nhalf of from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.75,0:30:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Say you want a coffee maker\Nthat costs 5,800 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.53,0:30:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}My point is,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.29,0:30:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}please be careful not to let me\Nfind out how much it really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.52,0:30:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Oh, this is fine,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.04,0:31:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}but it is like I am lying to you,\Nand it makes me feel guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.20,0:31:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}No. It's a lie if you consider\Nmy feelings and I find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.88,0:31:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}But if I don't find out,\Nit's kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.32,0:31:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}If you save up\Nto three kindnesses like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.12,0:31:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}it turns into love.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.56,0:31:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}On the contrary, if there is love,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.84,0:31:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}you can show me such kindness\Nthree times.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.43,0:31:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Oh, I mean just in one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.36,0:31:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Three times a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.76,0:31:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}That means, I can be kind to you\N1,095 times in a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.92,0:31:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It applies to the opposite case!\NIf you live up to 100 years old,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.76,0:31:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}then you can show me\Nsuch kindness 54,750 more times!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.68,0:31:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}You can do calculations so quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.70,0:31:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I can do all addition, subtraction,\Nmultiplication but not division.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.54,0:31:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I'm glad that we're married.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.30,0:31:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.78,0:31:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.22,0:31:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I just thought of that\Nwhen I looked at you just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.03,0:32:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}But your husband can't do division.\NEveryone will laugh at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.27,0:32:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Even if everyone laughs at me,\NI fell in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.15,0:32:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}So I can't leave you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.59,0:32:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.41,0:32:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}There were more varieties of things\Nat the supermarket we went to today.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.51,0:32:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Yeah, let's find out more places.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.39,0:32:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I found an interesting restaurant\Nright after we said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.93,0:32:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What is Bhutan cuisine?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.13,0:32:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I'll look it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.13,0:32:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Sir Tezuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.01,0:32:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- Take one.\N- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.13,0:32:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- Take one.\N- Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.93,0:32:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.99,0:32:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.07,0:32:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- Oh, what.\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.51,0:33:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}In 2018...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.55,0:33:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}You bump into your neighbours\Nquite often here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.07,0:33:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I came here to eat alone,\Nbut there are four people now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.43,0:33:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Hey, beer!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.39,0:33:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Beer!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.39,0:33:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- Oh, beer?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.67,0:33:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Would you please wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.89,0:33:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.97,0:33:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}This is very spicy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.41,0:33:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Bhutan cuisine seems to be\Nthe world's most spicy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.13,0:33:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.57,0:33:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Tell me, where did you two meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.37,0:33:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Well, both of our jobs\Nare sports-related.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.35,0:33:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}All right, so you met at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.19,0:33:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}No one I meet at work\Nfalls in love with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.85,0:33:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}that's why it's tough for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.61,0:33:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Nobody knows what you're talking\Nabout if you get angry suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.61,0:33:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It's obvious!\NI'm saying that I'm not popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.21,0:33:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.97,0:33:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I'm impressed\Nthat you got yourself a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.11,0:33:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}How did you get this young husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.03,0:33:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.11,0:33:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Oh, I pursued her relentlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.96,0:33:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}You pursued her?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.12,0:33:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I kept pursuing her,\Nbut she kept rejecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.91,0:33:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}About 30 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.91,0:33:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Thirty times? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.51,0:34:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Don't ask them every detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.11,0:34:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It's fine! She wants to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.08,0:34:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Obviously, our age gap,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.12,0:34:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}and I had divorced once too.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.35,0:34:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.63,0:34:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.76,0:34:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Change the channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.16,0:34:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Would you please wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.64,0:34:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.36,0:34:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It was found at another river...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.44,0:34:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It's the Doctor Yamagiwa you hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.72,0:34:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}That's why I want\Nto change the channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.60,0:34:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}You hate him? I quite like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.00,0:34:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}He doesn't just hate him. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.04,0:34:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Speaking of which,\Nwho drew my ballot paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.12,0:34:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.34,0:34:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Shota, try this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.14,0:34:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.94,0:34:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Fujii!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.06,0:34:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What? I have to change it myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.85,0:34:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Let's start.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.77,0:34:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Six buildings in Meguro were burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.47,0:34:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Anyway, many things happened\Nin the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.59,0:34:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}The doctor was his classmate\Nin college.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.39,0:34:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}He is no big deal as a doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.03,0:34:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}but it annoys me that he earns\Nso much as a celebrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.31,0:35:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}This will never end\Nif you kill him just for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.59,0:35:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}That's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.55,0:35:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What, for example?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.35,0:35:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What do you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.47,0:35:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Have you finally made up your mind\Nto marry Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.11,0:35:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Well, almost like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.63,0:35:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}You've been dating\Nsince you were students.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.87,0:35:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I'm amazed\Nthat she waited for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.83,0:35:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.67,0:35:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Well, she's the girl you loved\Noriginally, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.07,0:35:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What? She was just a cute junior\Nin the club I joined.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.99,0:35:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}But you confessed your love for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.95,0:35:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It's been a long time,\Nso I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.05,0:35:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}At that time, Kaoru asked me
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.57,0:35:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}to pretend to be her boyfriend\Nbecause you were too persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.23,0:35:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It was boring just to pretend.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.67,0:35:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}So I slept with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.31,0:35:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Well, whatever the reason was,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.45,0:36:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}you dated for a long time\Nand you'll finally get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.81,0:36:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.77,0:36:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}No, I'm dating an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.21,0:36:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}She's in the morning drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.09,0:36:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.93,0:36:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I'm thinking about marrying her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.39,0:36:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What about Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.25,0:36:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}That's why,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.81,0:36:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}it's time to go for Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.37,0:36:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Maybe even you can do it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.33,0:36:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Don't be afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.37,0:36:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}She won't cost you a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.33,0:36:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}even if you only have a modest\Nincome as a hospital doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.49,0:36:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}she isn't going to complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.37,0:36:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.35,0:36:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Mr Fujii?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.58,0:36:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I can still stand it\Nif it was only about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.26,0:36:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}but that's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.02,0:36:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.02,0:36:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It's not fun if I just kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.54,0:36:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I'll travel back in time
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.14,0:36:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}and kill Yamagiwa\Nwhen he was in college
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.38,0:36:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}and I'll start my life over again\Nin a world without him!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.26,0:36:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Mr Fujii!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.58,0:36:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I want to kill him more and more!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.58,0:36:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- Mr Fuji\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.78,0:37:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.02,0:37:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.58,0:37:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}It was identified{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.34,0:37:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}as the missing celebrity\Nand doctor,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.14,0:37:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}Yutaro Yamagiwa,\NDoctor Yamagiwa.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.50,0:37:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}Our reporter, Sasaki,\Nis at the scene{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.78,0:37:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}where the body was found.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.50,0:37:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}Dr Yutaro Yamagiwa's body\Nwas found here{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.22,0:37:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}in a forest in Isehara City,\NKanagawa Prefecture.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.06,0:37:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}In the forest 300 metres ahead,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.02,0:37:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}Dr Yamagiwa's body was found\Nburied underground.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.54,0:37:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.82,0:37:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Is it okay to leave Mr Fujii there?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.10,0:37:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Well, he wanted to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.94,0:37:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Anyway, Yamagiwa--
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.18,0:37:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Oh, hurry up! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.06,0:37:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.94,0:37:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.86,0:37:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.82,0:37:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}You two had better train\Nyour quadriceps muscles again!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.66,0:38:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Could he be killed\Nby one of the residents as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.70,0:38:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"As well'? Please don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.54,0:38:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.78,0:38:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.50,0:38:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Did you tell your husband\Nabout the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.66,0:38:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I didn't tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.78,0:38:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.46,0:38:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Xinyi.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.74,0:38:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}We're closing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.94,0:38:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Fujii, what about the rule?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.92,0:38:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Rule? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.58,0:38:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}If someone killed your target,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.15,0:38:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}you have to kill theirs.\NYou said this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.21,0:38:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I was joking. There is no such rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.65,0:38:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}You're saying\Nthat you won't kill anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.37,0:39:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Why do you only talk to me\Nso casually?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.25,0:39:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Fujii, just go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.99,0:39:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Someone killed the man\Nwhom you want dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.36,0:39:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}so you have to kill the person\Non the piece of paper you drew too,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.56,0:39:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}or you'll violate the rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.48,0:39:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Masao Tanaka"
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.32,0:39:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.80,0:40:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Obey the rules properly”
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.56,0:40:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Chiunque Kuramae"
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.36,0:40:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Room 501, Go Sano"
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.56,0:41:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- Morning.\N- Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.04,0:41:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}You bought more?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.40,0:41:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Yeah, there's a follow-up story\Nabout the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.20,0:41:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}In the news, it was only reported\Nthat the body was dismembered,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.88,0:41:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}but it seems that his head\Nhasn't been found, great detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.32,0:41:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I don't want to hear that\Nso early in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.62,0:41:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}The suspect hasn't been found--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.44,0:41:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Really, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.04,0:41:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.68,0:41:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It's okay. I should be the one\Nto apologise.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.00,0:41:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Dr Yamagiwa's Dead Body.\NWhere is his head?"
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.08,0:41:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Truth Weekly"
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.52,0:41:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}- Dr Fujii.\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.48,0:42:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.32,0:42:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}You'll open the plastic bag, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.72,0:42:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.16,0:42:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}You always tear it open.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.00,0:42:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}I look forward\Nto working with you today too.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.08,0:42:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Mr Atsushi Fujii"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.77,0:42:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Where is his head?"
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.55,0:42:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"It is your turn to kill."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.31,0:42:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Could he be killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.48,0:42:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}by one of the residents as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.83,0:42:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Fourth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.40,0:43:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.20,0:43:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.08,0:43:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}This.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.12,0:43:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.88,0:43:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"It is your turn to kill."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.52,0:43:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Lately, I've been getting them\Nevery day when I go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.75,0:43:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Something like this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.16,0:43:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Soliciting to murder"
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.84,0:43:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.20,0:43:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Ask the person who put it\Nthrough my door for details.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.88,0:43:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}And warn everyone\Nnot to play pranks like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.15,0:44:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}Last Monday,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.79,0:44:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fscx356\fscy342}celebrity and doctor,\NYutaro Yamagiwa's body was found...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.55,0:45:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Off"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.01,0:45:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.41,0:45:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Dr Yamagiwa\NWhere is his head?"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.57,0:45:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Your Turn to Kill"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.59,0:45:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"The next person to be killed is..."
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.83,0:45:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}It says that it's my turn to kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.95,0:45:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}Mr Fujii is getting\Nthreatening letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.91,0:45:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}"Rule of murder-swap"\NYou aren't thinking that
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.43,0:46:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}it's your turn to kill, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.55,0:46:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}This is ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.91,0:46:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx356\fscy342}The culprit has to be someone\Nfrom the residential tower.
